{"tid":89812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭稱參選為阻止憲制危機　免選出中央不任命的人","createTime":"2017-01-21T15:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T11:49:24.000Z","uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47818a171660051417d7a32678b0c86ea50d3cd3","tid":89812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"【特首跑馬仔】林鄭稱參選為阻止憲制危機　免選出中央不任命的人 <a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170121/s00001/1485011254115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170121%2Fs00001%2F1485011254115&d=s5dXgweWZRDygw1R3FA92XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e7695f19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170121%2Fs00001%2F1485011254115&h=6e4b361b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170121/s00001/1485011254115</a>"},{"pid":"365392ad1cc2a925a29b9de1a542ec133d6e1b7b","tid":89812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥昨日與傳媒高層的飯局上，被問及為何決定參選特首時解釋，特首選舉最壞情況，是選出一個中央不任命的人，這將是國際大新聞、大憲政危機，她有責任防止這大憲政危機出現。被問及為何其他參選人有機會不獲中央任命，林太只說中央對特首、司長、局長有不同要求，但沒有再詳細解說。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥競選辦公關戴健文回應查詢時稱，林太席間沒有提及任何人名，亦非針對任何人，林太當時只是說出特首的憲制角色，須同時向中央及特區政府負責，一旦選出的人不為中央接受，便會出現憲制危機，故決定參選。問及席間是否有人問到現時擬參選特首人士，既有退休法官及立法會議員，為何有中央不會任命的人，林太稱中央對特首、司長、局長有不同要求，戴健文稱他不記得。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華競選辦發言人稱，不評論傳聞，但期望選舉是君子之爭，按照基本法，以公平公正公開的形式進行。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀競選辦公室發言人指，不評論林太的說法，但期望有一個公平公正公開的選舉。"},{"pid":"cc2d909981088ad02af410211fa00a30ec228f8a","tid":89812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433edec12d8b7f7c65732141433e4ddc1a3530ec","tid":89812,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"咁不如唔好選，直接委任啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd41d50b2e5322b24517f6da3eba771f06a72b6","tid":89812,"uid":21024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"咁林太選乜柒姐 係咪都佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家係選香港小姐呀？"},{"pid":"2d4e034ae51546923fe79996272447a9750bea98","tid":89812,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"咁講即係中央冇任點你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60d7b3bca66fc40e936e069dc2947b761895c20","tid":89812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"佢咁講分分鐘得罪習總，rip"},{"pid":"30d395c11c51efeadeccaafd83209e801dddf63f","tid":89812,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"嘩，講乜撚呀，中央係尊重香港選舉架"},{"pid":"96134344563d1f56d4027aea5a5080ef31076238","tid":89812,"uid":51842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"屌！<br />\n成日用埋D on9理由去解畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850946dacf088e8c237cc27c507514ddb0813946","tid":89812,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"屌你 上面仲要靠香港去呃外資佬錢 家陣係唔係倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4633e3784f0baecd36af6e4cd24a014ad9b5a5","tid":89812,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚左線"},{"pid":"b466cca0bff7f178d933a1059fa66527198843a5","tid":89812,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"上帝呢?又話受感召參選既?做乜而家又話中共要自己入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi